    "SIX NavSta Contest Open For Plaque Design The Naval Station is asking its military and cisilian xrsonnl for a design for a Naval Station plaque An award of a 25 I S Savings Bond will be gisen to the person submitting the winning design In announcing the competition to establish a design which will be used to represent the Naal Station as a decorative plaque the Nasal Station has asked its permanently attached militars and civilian personnel to submit their proposed designs for considera tion bv a panel of judges ASW Council niMtltion rules state that the design shall be enclosed in a shield r circle approximately six to eight inches in diameter in black ami white or color ami should reflect the Naval Station s mission of logistic support to the forces afloat ami the components of the Naval Base or alter natively contain a symbol that would be particularly applicable Such symbols include the Con stellation or the bronze cannons in front of the Headquarters Building The design which will be cast in a mold should be kept relative ly simple Deadline Deadline for design entries which will be submitted to the Administrative Assistant to the Executive Officer"
